div.div: v0.3.0 - QoL Update Unavailable attacks still show up Unavailable attacks are now red Combat sidebar no longer shows in main menu Targets now update if the text changes Inputs now update if the text changes The critical hit notification is now orange-red Added number formatting with commas Siderbar now shows # of level ups available Fixed Groundpount typo In some menu, if you can only take 1 item, you no longer have to specify an amount You can now equip armor Possibly fixed XP share Log now updates whenever you take an action or every 10th tick Added level styling through level 100 and edited some of styling Added button to view your vault in the character menu Adjusted consumable stats Added useful descriptions to consumables Added bestiary Now exits containers if empty

section.div: v0.2.0 - Maybe, possibly, actually this time Fixed take all Added selling items at a mark up Blacksmith now sells iron bars Added the woods Moved some campfire recipes to the grove Added traders Can now sell to the blacksmith Added Mysterious Trader You can now drop items Added XP share Buffed some enemies from the last update Low-level enemies spawn less on lower floors Dungeon min floors increased: 5 -> 7 Dungeon max floors increased: 7 -> 9 Added teleporation scrolls Added bank Added vaults Fixed weapon switching not updating attacks issue Logs to coal no longer gives XP Consumables are actually consumed now Fixed directions Added a line break before CON in the level up menu Added a forsaken place Players can now start the beginning of the end 8 new monsters 17 new items 3 new dungeon objects
